DRIVE MOTORS: AM 18 bi Thrust

HULL STRESS FACTOR: T ko 28

HYPERSPACE CAPABILITY: Yes


ASP MK II:
Galactic Navy vessel designed and manufactured in government
workshops, incorporating secret self-destruct devices which are
primed to activate when the astrogation controls are used by
unfamiliar hands.  Integument has chameleon properties enabling the
ship to assume effective camouflage in any type of environment.
Intended for reconnaissance and the transport of high-ranking
military personnel from combat it is very fast and manoeuvrable.
Despite its hazardous nature it makes an ideal pirate vessel,
primarily because of the speed, camouflage and high intensity
Hassoni-Kruger Burst-lasers. The Asp II has room for powerful shield
generators, but only one missile pod.

DIMENSIONS: 70/20/65 ft

