COBRA MK III:
Larger, more popular version of the Cobra Mk 1 (the Mk 2 only reached
prototype stage and was abandoned due to a design fault in the hull).
This ship is equipped with several special features, including Zieman
Energy Deflection Shields, fore and aft, and mounting for four Ingram
Pulse lasers. The Cobra is much favoured by lone-wolf traders who
wish to combine potential superior combat qualities with adequate
cargo space.

