FER-DE-LANCE:
A Zorgon Petterson Group (Zee Pee Gee) designed vessel favoured by
well-heeled bounty hunters and freewheeling business corporations.
A sophisticated craft, capable of both limited trading, combat,
and leisure function. The spacious hull is mainly given over to
sophisticated weaponry, defences and navigation equipment at the
expense of cargo capacity. Cabin accommodation is large & luxurious
with extensive Owndirt Inc. Recycling facilities, encouraging
extended live-in periods (useful whilst pursuing a quarry). Fuel
scoop is a standard fitting, ensuring complete self-sufficiency.

