KRAIT:
Small, reliable one-man fighter, common until the standardised
version of the Mamba became available on the open market. Several of
these early Faulcon deLacy designed craft may still be found in
service in remote areas, but spare parts are no longer available and
the need to cannibalise has reduced numbers still further in recent
 years.

